1. Install vscode deb from official website
2. Install extensions: c/c++, go, python, vim emulation, github copilot, codex
3. Login to github copilot with github account
4. Sign in to ChatGPT for codex
5. File -> Preferences -> Keyboard Shortcuts, refer to system-key-shortcut
6. Press “ctrl+shift+p” and search “preferences: open user settings (json)”, refer to vim-extension-config

